{"tid":1486574,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"參議員查克舒默發表最新推文支持香港民眾","createTime":"2019-08-19T02:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T02:28:59.000Z","uid":140655,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"946ecf0b1837d0f74b4076d90e415dca2145856b","tid":1486574,"uid":140655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:10:51.000Z","msg":"8月19日，參議員查克舒默發表最新推文支持香港民眾。推文內容：「美國聽得到香港民眾的聲音。習近平加強了對香港民主運動的鎮壓而川普總統沒有站出來反對他，這是不能被接受的。中國共產黨必須接受懲罰。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSC4Lbb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSC4Lbb.png&h=d2cc422b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChuck Schumer (@SenSchumer) 已推文：America hears the people of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nPresident @realDonaldTrump: It is unacceptable that you are not standing up to President Xi as he intensifies his crackdown on democratic rights in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nThe Chinese Communist Party must face consequences.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/QisBAgNdyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQisBAgNdyo&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSspnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=0080e00d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/QisBAgNdyo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenSchumer/status/1163149553736015872?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenSchumer%2Fstatus%2F1163149553736015872%3Fs%3D20&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSspnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=f67a5c80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenSchumer%2Fstatus%2F1163149553736015872%3Fs%3D20&h=1b1fc738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenSchumer/status/1163149553736015872?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"b81fcb82d2e7f34b67c120d207f51f2fe66ac01f","tid":1486574,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429e